title: Female Sign

nouns: A woman is a female human.
An animal of the sex that produces eggs.
An adult human member of the sex that produces ova and bears young.
An adult female person (as opposed to a man)
A gender symbol denotes the sex of an organism or characterizes an agent by gender.

description: A circle shown with a crossed vertical line beneath it, used as a representation for women. Often used on International Women's Day.
